'''Naruyamcha''' is a member of Narutofan forums. His life is a tale of [[cutting|anguish, rejection and misogyny]]. He is well known for being an [[emo]] par excellence, weirdly avid [[sport]]s fan, transparent suck-up as well as many other [[homosexual epithets|unflattering epithets]]. His sheer hopelessness cannot be fully fathomed unless you have interacted with him.

Naru hates it when people get laid more often than he does.

