== Naruyamcha In A Nutshell ==
Naruyamcha starts off in his interaction with people as being generally friendly and pandering. However, this is almost always subject to change.

If the interactee in question is female, he will invariably "fall in love" with her. This love may or may not be affection as opposed to a bid to get into the girl's e-pants, but regardless, this 'love' is always very, very creepy. Naru begins to make unwelcome sexual advances and requests for pictures. His clumsy double entendres and generally stalkerish mannerisms are usually rejected with tact by the girl, but this will not deter him from making more.

More lulz ensue when the object of his affections has a boyfriend. In this case Naru will try to pretend that this boyfriend either does not exist, or make various painful 'slips' when referring to him. This happens IN ALL CASES.

*<naruyamcha> the best *coughworstcough* thing is here

*<naruyamcha> her lose..... I mean, e-bf

Naru somehow thinks this is very smart and funny.

In addition to this, Naru is an incredibly gullible person, becoming easily-fooled by anyone of the female gender. Numerous times as he been tricked by women that tell him intimate details, such as their masturbation habits, to arouse him and get his hopes up shortly before shooting him down.

Several times, Naruyamcha has been caught making sexual advances to minors, in ways such as telling a fifteen year-old girl (fourteen at the time) that he '''loved how wide her hips are'''. He has also attempted to force himself upon a seventeen year-old through the internet, several times having attempted to '''e-rape''' the young girl. This is all between his constant pestering of naked photographs of said women. At twenty-eight years of age, the man knows no boundaries to his sexual harassment.

