== The Penis Incident ==
Very much self-explanatory - Naruyamcha posts a picture of his penis in the Sexy Pictures thread on NF. The masses' response to this utter horror was that of unanimous Dismay. Several people even commented that his penis looked '''diseased'''. It has been compared to a likeness of a shriveled, half-eaten mushroom. Naruyamcha, sensing that the girls weren't falling over their heels to impale themselves on his diseased dick, removed the picture, and lied, stating that the picture was his '''brother's''' penis.

Please read the second-last sentence again. '''His brother's''' penis.

