== Naruyamcha In 2008 ==
As of recently, Naruyamcha has kept activity in the Blender at NarutoForums among other places. It seems that his womanly-hating ways have changed very little - although more vocal, his style has been tamed somewhat. The seething rage is still quite evident, however. Most recently, an anonymous NarutoForum member has made a Legendary Statistics Card for Naruyamcha. It is believed that this is an accurate representation of Naruyamcha and all he stands for.

In recent times Naruyamcha has shown an affinity to the art of licking the ass hole of the female. Also known as rimming, analingus or in more colloquially 'the rim job'. He tried to do this on MSN with a declared lesbian who despite telling repeatedly that her girlfriend would not approve, he still expressed his great and genuine desire to 'lick her hot white ass hole'. This conversation was subsequently forwarded to a friend of hers and upon being posted on NarutoForums, many lulz were had.

